$ VS Code: Workspace Trust

{ Restricted mode #vs-code-restricted-mode

  { Indication of restricted mode

    Being in restricted mode is indicated by this line in the GUI's top …
    gh|about-VS-Code|/workspace/trust/restricted-mode/img/top.png|| 

    … and the explicit note in the GUI's bottem left corner:
    gh|about-VS-Code|/workspace/trust/restricted-mode/img/bottom-left.png|| 

  }
  { Misc

    The → development/editors/Visual-Studio-Code/settings_json[setting] `security.workspace.trust.untrustedFiles`.

  }

}
